OL,3,CFather and son guilty of killing boy,
OL,4,C4, in hit and run
OL,6,FA father and son from Kent have been
OL,7,Ffound guilty of killing a four-year-
OL,8,Fold family member in a hit and run
OL,9,Fnear Dartford in Kent.
OL,11,FPeter Maughan died when a 4x4 he was a
OL,12,Fpassenger in, was rammed in Southfleet
OL,13,Fon 1 June 2025 after a chase on the A2.
OL,15,FThe driver of the car Owen Maughan,
OL,16,F27, and his father, Patrick Maughan,
OL,17,F54, were found not guilty of murder at
OL,18,FMaidstone Crown Court.
