OL,6,FOwen Maughan had already admitted
OL,7,Fmanslaughter, and pled guilty to
OL,8,Finflicting GBH and causing serious
OL,9,Finjury by dangerous driving to Peter's
OL,10,Ffather Lovell Mahon.
OL,12,FThe court heard how Peter's father
OL,13,FLovell Mahon was seriously injured in
OL,14,Fthe collision, and his mother Hayley
OL,15,FMaughan and one-year-old sister
OL,16,FAnnarica Maughan, were also in the car.
OL,18,FPatrick Maughan was today found guilty
OL,19,Fof manslaughter and inflicting
OL,20,Fgrevious bodily harm to Lovell Mahon.
